column5: Good day from Eagle River,Ont.Always enjoy my trips through town
Cool. My family had some friends, the Grahams, who lived in Eagle River for a few years. Bill
Nice picture. Merry Christmas to all!
Great little town.Great shortcut coming from hwy 502.Few more months and will get busy through there again.
We're you down to eagle Xmas shopping for the wife and ME!!
Thanks for posting this John, i like the shortcut.

Look of folks don't realize it's there.Nice drive through the reserve.Have you taken the drive to the pow wow grounds and beach.Heck of a veiw of Eagles east end.It comes out on Ojibway drive again.Worth the look.
No I'll have to check it out, thanks.
Been through there several times on my way to Deer Trail Lodge on Waldhof bay back in the 90's. Nice scenic little town.
